        <div class="max-w-3xl text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg 2xl:text-lg leading-snug sm:leading-normal text-white text-center">
          Jeremy Whitley is a writer from Durham, NC. He is the writer/creator of <i>The Dog Knight</i>, <i>Princeless</i>, <i>The School for Extraterrestrial Girls</i>, and <i>Navigating with You</i>. He is also the writer of over fifty issues of <i>My Little Pony</i> comics including <i>Nightmare Knights</i>, <i>Siege of the Crystal Empire</i>, and Season 10. He was once bitten by a radioactive pegasus.
        </div>
      </div>
