          Rena Anakwe
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-3xl text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg 2xl:text-lg leading-snug sm:leading-normal text-white text-center">
          Rena Anakwe is a Nigerian-Canadian-American voice actor, interdisciplinary artist and performer based in Brooklyn, New York. She is best known as the voice of Sapphire Shores on <i>My Little Pony: Friendship is Magic</i> and Janai on <i>The Dragon Prince</i>.
